utten happy. Men uansett. Keep on walking, Johnny Walker."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "93ed949491310dc1a196af16258a63a1f34c0bcf6177b35b48f5f7f56da0366a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-04-16T10:42:21.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Surrealistisk, apokalyptisk folkeeventyr der grandiose overdrivelser og \u00f8m poesi lever side om side."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/scene/article12611207.ece/9a1db5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Kappe-037.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/41a6327cbc8a0c24cba9bcfeda31c6ed0b119b00.jpg?58ca7cc9"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Holder s\u00e5 det suser i skogen -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "41a6327cbc8a0c24cba9bcfeda31c6ed0b119b00"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "kultur"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["stykke", "fryktelig d\u00e5rlig", "liv", "lever", "skogen", "on walking", "teater", "oppsetning"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["moby dick", "everybody", "the marcels", "talkin", "royal garden", "studioscenen", "blue", "r\u00f8dhette", "keep", "dager", "tr\u00f8ndelag teater", "sitting on the dock of dubai", "sn\u00f8", "r\u00f8d"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "prince"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["karl-vidar lende", "lisa lie", "hildegunn eggen", "johnny walker", "ole johan skjelbred", "kathrine thorborg johansen", "harry nilssons"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss", "pluss/kultur"]}, {"field": "og-image"